<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<title><%= title %></title>
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/bootstrap.min.css" />
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/DT_bootstrap.css" />
</head>
<body>
	<div class="container">
		<div class="hero-unit">
			<h1><%= title %></h1>
			<p>The Game is based on the idea discussed 
				<a href="http://mathwithbaddrawings.com/2013/06/16/ultimate-tic-tac-toe/" target="_blank">here</a>.</p>
		</div>
		<h3>List of Open Rooms : </h3>
		<table class="table table-striped" id="gamestable">
			<thead>
				<tr><th>#</th><th>Room Name</th><th>Status</th><th>Action</th></tr>
			</thead>
			<tbody id="games">

			</tbody>
		</table>
		<div class="well">
			<h5>README</h5>
			<h6>WHAT</h6>
			<ul>
				<li>To create a new room, append some text to the URL. Or, let me do that for you. <a href="<%= rand %>" id="newgame" target="_blank">Click here</a>.</li>
				<li>Action: <span class="btn-small btn-success">Join</span> <i class="icon-arrow-right"></i> The Room needs one more player.</li>
				<li>Action: <span class="btn-small btn-warning">View</span> <i class="icon-arrow-right"></i> The Room is already full. But you can view the game play <span class="label label-info">live</span>.</li>
			</ul>
			<h6>HOW</h6>
			<ul>
				<li><a href="http://mathwithbaddrawings.com/2013/06/16/ultimate-tic-tac-toe/" target="_blank">It's here</a></li>
			</ul>
			<h6>WHAT ELSE</h6>
			<ul>
				<li>When there is no one in the Room, and you Join, you become <span class="label label-info">Player X</span>. So, in any room, <span class="label label-info">Player X</span> starts the game.</li>
				<li>When <span class="label label-info">Player X</span> is in the Room, and you Join, you become <span class="label label-info">Player O</span></li>
				<li>When the Room is <strong>Full</strong>, and you Join, you become a guest and you can view the game play live.</li>
				<li>When the room has no active players for sometime, it'll be <span class="label label-important"> deleted</span> automatically.</li>
			</ul>
			<h6>WHO</h6>
			<ul>
				<li>Boopathi Rajaa ( <a href="http://boopathi.in" target="_blank">boopathi.in</a> | <a href="https://github.com/boopathi" target="_blank">Github</a> ) </li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</div>
	<script src="/js/jquery.min.js"></script>
	<script src="/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
	<script>
	var DATA;
	$(function() {
		DATA = JSON.parse($("<div/>").html("<%= data %>").text());
	});
	</script>
	<script src="/js/jquery.dataTables.min.js"></script>
	<script src="/js/DT_bootstrap.js"></script>
	<script src="/js/homepage.js"></script>
</body>
</html>